name.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: WCL DK Analyzer for Cataclysm Classic

short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Tool to analyze WCL logs for WoW Cataclysm Classic Frost and Unholy DKs

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This package uses Warcraft Logs to create detailed raid analysis for Unholy and Frost DKs. Original project created by Ducks for Wrath of the Lich King, updated for Cataclysm by Waives.
